{"tid":82691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劇本已經編定，品客叔叔唔會贏","createTime":"2017-01-16T06:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-16T07:50:56.000Z","uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"feb5271c90ce4c7aeecf431fb790cddda91c9396","tid":82691,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:50:41.000Z","msg":"而家俾佢唔撈財政，係俾下個假希望你啲香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你地以為佢會大熱當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最終當然冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中央要咁做就係想無形咁同你班人講，係你自己放棄2017一人一票，品客冇得做都唔到你怨，係你班人自己放棄揀嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要成個幾月先俾佢唔撈？因為呢個月要同曬有得選嗰千幾人溝通，確保佢唔會贏到先放佢出黎選囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭盔<br />\n1我好似政治中立<br />\n2發夢諗到"},{"pid":"a78df52d8da6099cf3c39ddccafa464e2bba90d6","tid":82691,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:52:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72fcf0b0d39534602c35ce200540d3cf3877e762","tid":82691,"uid":9460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T06:56:23.000Z","msg":"邏輯好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6f0d0f7be8bc5e2420b9adae1bd758869d5ceb","tid":82691,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db1c19633808ecf3bfe80ba21f4fb02b433d7670","tid":82691,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:11:49.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31286c2c1b80c51661b72d9ea4bae2a92790a30","tid":82691,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邏輯好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登仔有邏輯既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32be500186722a06d86af35147eb4da722394cc","tid":82691,"uid":18795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:13:57.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"0aea064d4d3f214a8b5fdfe0e6d8c045c8fb0815","tid":82691,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邏輯好怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登仔有邏輯既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係高登會員<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d30a982999bc3b3a9927d1a6c2991906c4a3330f","tid":82691,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:20:37.000Z","msg":"雜種唔係主動搵佢扼手咩?"},{"pid":"4e0d5ce548c96f5e196cebdc593f0d98bb253537","tid":82691,"uid":15548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:21:26.000Z","msg":"睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90fa529c29d0aa5efead939eb2a7a511ec1375ac","tid":82691,"uid":42122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家俾佢唔撈財政，係俾下個假希望你啲香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你地以為佢會大熱當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最終當然冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中央要咁做就係想無形咁同你班人講，係你自己放棄2017一人一票，品客冇得做都唔到你怨，係你班人自己放棄揀嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要成個幾月先俾佢唔撈？因為呢個月要同曬有得選嗰千幾人溝通，確保佢唔會贏到先放佢出黎選囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n頭盔<br />\n1我好似政治中立<br />\n2發夢諗到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n薯片同林鄭同時獲放行，似乎只有一個原因可以解釋，就係薯片辭職時，佢亞爺通知佢唔會咁快批，因為要等埋林鄭，所以薯片先會係記者會話「現階段唔可以講太多」，係Facebook叫人be claimed, 兼且繼續落區做親民show.<br />\n<br />\n而佢亞爺就利用呢個月時間DQ埋689，可能再同西環講明，「今次我地每邊派一個人出來，邊個輸入，以後係香港就要收口。」所以而家小明仲在位，而且西環繼續係背後幫自己既人拉票。<br />\n<br />\n而林鄭宣佈辭職時同時表示會去選，似乎係玩擦邊球，想搶返過去一個月蝕左比薯片既時間。<br />\n<br />\n所以今次選舉，可能係一個真正既選舉，係類似美國民主，共和兩黨咁，各派一個代表出來玩，輸左嗰邊以後係香港要收聲只不過分別係唔可以公開背後既關係，同埋香港市民無份玩咁解。<br />\n<br />\nBtw 我幾時都覺得中共兩派應該分成兩個黨，明刀明槍咁鬥。"}]}